# Project Structure Rules

## Main Entry Points
- Main application: [App.svelte](mdc:src/App.svelte)
- Type definitions: [types.ts](mdc:src/types.ts)
- Build configuration: [svelte.config.js](mdc:svelte.config.js)
- Package configuration: [package.json](mdc:package.json)

## Component Organization
- Components directory: [src/components/](mdc:src/components/)
- Main components:
  - [FileUpload.svelte](mdc:src/components/FileUpload.svelte) - File upload functionality
  - [LogControls.svelte](mdc:src/components/LogControls.svelte) - Log filtering and controls
  - [LogDisplay.svelte](mdc:src/components/LogDisplay.svelte) - Log display and rendering

## File Naming Conventions
- Components: PascalCase (e.g., `LogDisplay.svelte`)
- Utilities: camelCase (e.g., `types.ts`)
- Configuration: kebab-case (e.g., `svelte.config.js`)

## Project Type
- **VK Calls JS SDK Logs Analyzer** - Analyzes VK Calls JavaScript SDK logs
- Uses Svelte 5 with TypeScript
- Vite build system
- Monospace font styling for log display